    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/\">Mathematics in Lean</a> (repository <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathematics_in_lean\">here</a>) has been bumped to v4.20.0. It has a <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/C06_Discrete_Mathematics.html\">new chapter</a> on formalizing discrete mathematics, and the <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/C05_Elementary_Number_Theory.html#more-induction\">last section</a> of the previous chapter is also new. </p>\n<p>Patrick and I are pleased that MIL has been holding up o.k., but it needs some care. We will make some updates and revisions this summer, address issues, introduce new tactics and automation, and so on.</p>",
